Collections.rule:
Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@B*))
Types: Tag
Facts: tagName @B*
Facts: hasGameTag @A*(rdf:ID)

Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@B*))
Types: Feature
Facts: featureName @B*
Facts: hasGameFeature @A*(rdf:ID)

Individual: @L*(mm:hashEncode)
Types: Player
Facts: foaf:nick @L*
Facts: userReview @L* (rdf:ID=(@G*,"_",@J*))

Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@B*))
Types: Genre
Facts: genreName @B*
Facts: hasGameGenre @A*(rdf:ID)

Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@B*))
Types: Publisher
Facts: publisherName @B*
Facts: isPublishedBy @A*(rdf:ID)

Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@B*))
Types: Developer
Facts: developerName @B*
Facts: isDevelopedBy @A*(rdf:ID)

Individual: @B*(rdf:ID=(@B*))
Types: Franchise
Facts: franchiseName @B*
Facts: belongsToGameFranchise @A*(rdf:ID)

Individual: @J*(rdf:ID=(@G*,"_",@J*))
Types: Review
Facts: text @K*
Facts: hours @F* (xsd:decimal)
Facts: products @H*
Facts: publishingDate @B* (xsd:date)
Facts: recommended @I* (xsd:boolean)
Facts: reviewEarlyAccess @C* (xsd:boolean)
Facts: gameReview @G*(rdf:ID)

Individual: @F*(rdf:ID=(@F*))
Types: Game
Facts: about @A*
Facts: description @B*
Facts: earlyAccess @D* (xsd:boolean)
Facts: price @I* (xsd:float)
Facts: releaseDate @J* (xsd:date)
Facts: title @L*
